name: Nessy the Rilla - The Bull Song

metadata.description:
Nessy The Rilla is an Top-10 Billboard Music NFT artist from Detroit, Michigan that has created music for over 13 years performing alongside numerous mainstream artists. Nessy has made his mark in web3 by collaborating with NFT communities producing anthems + theme songs. 

In the midst of one of the biggest dips in the bear market, Nessy created The Bull Song as an attempt to revive the spirit of the space with a fun and vibrant track that you can't resist dancing to.
